  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nCurrently, forge has its own chain name and id list here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/forge-std/blob/cffb5628775fbf120bfc3c123149f6a6d99dc275/src/StdChains.sol#L182\r\n\r\nIt is different from what all other EVM tools use:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-lists/chains\r\n\r\nThis causes confusion for the users.\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n- Figure out what would be the best path to standardisation\r\n- If standardisation does not make sense, then highlight the supported chain names and differences in the documentation",
